room_title: Escape room "Outbreak 2020" by Epoch Escapes in Jefferson City
room_address: 3600 Country Club Dr #318 Jefferson City, MO 65109
room_description: It's a tale as old as time. You went to the hospital for a routine procedure, but when you awake, things are... different. Still inside the hospital, you and your group of fellow patients quickly realize civilization is no more; you now live in a world populated with flesh eating zombies! Locate the antidote and save yourselves before time runs out!
